latestIgtvVideos.title: UNBOXING My “New” Apple HomePod 🖲
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
On my free time from the world of makeup, I’m a huge tech/Apple geek. I purchased a lightly used Space Grey Apple HomePod online and I wanted to show an unboxing as there aren’t as many videos of this product unboxed by a non-professional audiophile or content creator. 
I’m also just super excited to share my risky purchase despite all the mixed reviews on this product. I’m by no means an expert on audio products.
I just wanted to have fun making content non-makeup related. 
Let me know if you like these type of videos! Thanks!
Song: Chill Days by Lakey Inspired @lakeyinspired
@apple @applemusic 
#homepod #apple #unboxing #unboxinghomepod #applemusic #spacegreyhomepod

latestIgtvVideos.title: Unboxing MAC Asia-exclusive Lightful-C + Coral Grass Products 🖤🌏
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
I purchased these items (full price! 5000 PHP) from a family member who visited the Philippines. I have tried the powder foundation when it was in the smaller compact but I just had to have the new pill–shaped compact. 
The powder is in the shade NC25 and has SPF 30/PA++++. I also got the new tinted primer that has SPF 45 / PA ++++. I would love to make more videos like this for fun! Enjoy my MAC Friends and beauty lovers 🧖🏼‍♀️💄
(Filmed on my trusty iPad 📲)
